<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContente9e27b54e33a43b7bd88cbc56b50d864">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="Papworth discharge" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_SummaryAndPhotoModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=1415"/>
</div>
</div>
<p>Why choose Royal Papworth Hospital</p>
<p>Royal Papworth Hospital is the UK’s largest specialist cardiothoracic hospital and the country’s main heart and lung transplant centre treating over 22,400 inpatient and day cases and 48,400 outpatients each year from across the UK.</p>
<p>Our patients travel long distances to see us, confident in the knowledge that we are at the forefront of providing new and innovative treatments for heart and lung patients.</p>
<p>Why do our patients choose Papworth?<br/>Committed to providing an excellent patient experienceWe achieve some of the best outcomes in the world for our patients. Our cardiothoracic services are internationally recognisedWe have an outstanding reputation for innovation and leading edge research. We retain an excellent record on infection prevention and controlWe are regarded as a top healthcare employer</p>
<p>About the Hospital<br/>Clinical Quality<br/>Facts &amp; figures<br/>Equality and Diversity<br/>New Papworth Hospital<br/>Governance<br/>Cambridge University Health Partners<br/>Our Performance and Annual Report<br/>Foundation Trust Members and Governors</p></div>
